'''Mij Rawd''' was the Vice-President of Marketing for [[Ardees/Legends|Ardees]].

In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], Rawd denied that the endorsement with [[Grav-ball/Legends|grav-ball]] athlete [[Deme Tryshyn]] was a defensive measure against the popular campaign from rival [[Lopez Drinks]] featuring musical artist [[Gaeriel Capens]].

